I promise you,
I have done worse.

00:22.773 --> 00:23.853
D'avin?

00:24.441 --> 00:25.601
(GRUNTING)

00:26.068 --> 00:27.103
Your brother.

00:27.694 --> 00:28.774
He tried to kill me.

00:29.112 --> 00:30.192
You need to shake
this off, D'av.

00:30.280 --> 00:31.690
