the green light to
serve you poison again.

01:15.784 --> 01:17.445
Looks like you need it.

01:18.245 --> 01:19.280
How's the team?

01:19.454 --> 01:20.739
Well, that's the problem.

01:22.499 --> 01:24.160
D’avin’s bare/y left
the ship.

01:27.337 --> 01:30.329
