I've already taken out
a warrant in your name.

02:25.562 --> 02:27.803
John”.
Uh-uh-uh...
It's done.

02:28.190 --> 02:31.648
Go see Bellus.
Trust me, you'll have fun.

02:35.405 --> 02:36.986
You're right.

02:37.074 --> 02:39.190
He's right. We've got to
get past this.

02:39.910 --> 02:41.866
It's fine.
The warrant is all.

02:47.459 --> 02:48.494
Hey.

02:50.796 --> 02:51.831
