04:49.456 --> 04:50.866
Hi, Bellus.

04:51.875 --> 04:52.990
Got your warrant
in the back.

04:53.210 --> 04:54.666
What is it?
Easy transpo.

04:54.795 --> 04:57.002
Bring the package back to
Westerley in one piece.

04:57.088 --> 05:00.455
Shouldn't be too hard,
even with your team
in the shitter.

05:01.718 --> 05:03.583
