05:25.700 --> 05:27.201
As hard as you want.
(GROANS)

05:32.374 --> 05:33.955
Dutch.

05:34.042 --> 05:37.159
Are you sure you're ready
to get back into the saddle
with this guy?

05:37.254 --> 05:38.790
If I'm not, I'm going
to find out.

05:39.297 --> 05:42.130
Nobody actually takes
the free shot. It's kind of
more of a gesture.

05:42.592 --> 05:43.627
Here's your warrant.

05:44.261 --> 05:45.296
Enjoy.

05:46.513 --> 05:48.925
Hurry back,
the rain's coming.

05:49.891 --> 05:51.267
(SlGHS)

05:55.939 --> 05:57.145
Wester/yns!

