06:58.418 --> 07:01.285
Uh... (EXHALES)
Pawter... (GROANS)
Pawter.

07:07.344 --> 07:09.926
Whoa, whoa, whoa, hey,
red, where do you think
you're going?

07:10.013 --> 07:11.844
Medical supplies.
Look, I'm sorry, Pawter.

07:11.932 --> 07:13.797
