08:35.557 --> 08:37.764
Company security.
Hands on your head.

08:39.310 --> 08:42.347
One-three-two, Center,
this is Captain
Hector Feraanz.

08:42.689 --> 08:44.850
Come back.
Easy.

08:46.484 --> 08:48.770
