my doctor friend.

12:00.511 --> 12:01.546
How?

12:01.888 --> 12:03.628
I know my way
around gunshots.

12:04.307 --> 12:06.468
You better make sure
she saves him.

12:17.153 --> 12:18.313
Pawter, I need my...

12:18.988 --> 12:20.524
Looking for this?

12:21.658 --> 12:23.865
It's all yours.
I'm just here
to help the Doc.

12:27.997 --> 12:30.488
