Okay.

12:35.046 --> 12:37.378
D'AVIN: So, we just
bring back that thing?

12:38.091 --> 12:40.628
Yep, easy Level 1.

12:40.718 --> 12:43.050
We should be home and out
of each other's hair soon.

12:44.681 --> 12:46.387
I didn't mean it like that.
Yeah.

12:46.516 --> 12:47.505
(SYSTEM BEEPING)

12:48.268 --> 12:49.883
Emergency system
is lighting up.

12:50.019 --> 12:51.930
Something big is tearing
through Old Town.

12:52.021 --> 12:53.761
