that close already.

12:54.357 --> 12:57.895
LUCY: A stage-four
black rain event has
touched down in Old Town,

12:58.027 --> 13:00.109
sector 113 to 150.

13:00.196 --> 13:03.029
Travel and communications
will be affected
for the duration.

13:03.116 --> 13:04.356
Communications?

13:04.450 --> 13:06.532
What kind of storm
are we talking about?
Lethal.

13:06.619 --> 13:09.156
Company stripped the Badlands
and left a toxic graveyard
behind.

13:09.247 --> 13:10.407
All that pollution,

13:10.540 --> 13:14.158
