a heat wave whips it into
an electro-acid rain storm.

13:14.252 --> 13:15.287
Falling on John's head?

13:15.378 --> 13:17.369
He'll be fine at The Royale.
Pree knows his business.

13:18.548 --> 13:21.085
Well, ifthis monster's
what we're facing,
should we stay on Leith

13:22.218 --> 13:23.378
