13:35.064 --> 13:36.895
(MONITOR BEEPING)

13:39.694 --> 13:41.059
JOHN: Pawter.
Damn it.

13:42.030 --> 13:43.486
Hey, maybe back up
a little bit, huh?

13:43.573 --> 13:45.234
